    "description": "Welcome to Fabled Style, the multistyle VR rhythm game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game focuses on striking notes on the beat of the music using different Warrior Styles. Each Warrior Style has it's own weapons and control scheme. During a song the active Warrior Style can change multiple times to make things more interesting.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game currently includes 3 Warrior Styles: <br />\r\n- Brawler: Punch notes using your fists<br />\r\n- Gun Slinger: Shoot at notes using your guns<br />\r\n- Shield Master: Block notes using your shields<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are 2 gameplay modes:<br />\r\n- Quick play: Quickly and freely play songs<br />\r\n- Quest mode: Take on challenges<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are a total of 9 songs included at the moment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOther features:<br />\r\n- Custom songs support (view website for download link to song editor)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFuture updates of the game will include more Warrior Styles &amp; songs.",
